metadata.name: Heroin: The 2013 FBI Raid on Silk Road
metadata.description: A Bitcoin yellow brick road, heroin poppy fields, an Emerald City made of syringes, and the Silk Road camel, captured by the Good Witch of the West - J. Edgar Hoover, the first and longest serving director of the FBI. This NFT represents the FBI raid of Silk Road in 2013.
